#. <section class="sutta" id="sn56.5"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn56.5:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 56"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 56"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.5:0.2"
msgid "1. Samādhivagga"
msgstr "1. Immersion"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn56.5:0.3"
msgid "5. Paṭhamasamaṇabrāhmaṇasutta"
msgstr "5. Ascetics and Brahmins (1st)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn56.5:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Ye hi keci, bhikkhave, atītamaddhānaṃ samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā yathābhūtaṃ "
"abhisambojjhiṃsu, sabbe te cattāri ariyasaccāni yathābhūtaṃ abhisambojjhiṃsu."
msgstr "“Mendicants, whatever ascetics and brahmins truly wake up—in the past,"

msgctxt "sn56.5:1.2"
msgid ""
"Ye hi keci, bhikkhave, anāgatamaddhānaṃ samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā yathābhūtaṃ "
"abhisambojjhissanti, sabbe te cattāri ariyasaccāni yathābhūtaṃ "
"abhisambojjhissanti."
msgstr "future,"

msgctxt "sn56.5:1.3"
msgid ""
"Ye hi keci, bhikkhave, etarahi samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā yathābhūtaṃ "
"abhisambojjhanti, sabbe te cattāri ariyasaccāni yathābhūtaṃ abhisambojjhanti."
msgstr "or present—all of them truly wake up to the four noble truths."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli5.417"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn56.5:2.1"
msgid "Katamāni cattāri?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "sn56.5:2.2"
msgid "Dukkhaṃ ariyasaccaṃ … pe … dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā ariyasaccaṃ."
msgstr ""
"The noble truths of suffering, the origin of suffering, the cessation of "
"suffering, and the practice that leads to the cessation of suffering. …"

msgctxt "sn56.5:2.3"
msgid ""
"Ye hi keci, bhikkhave, atītamaddhānaṃ samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā yathābhūtaṃ "
"abhisambojjhiṃsu … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn56.5:2.4"
msgid "abhisambojjhissanti … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn56.5:2.5"
msgid ""
"abhisambojjhanti, sabbe te imāni cattāri ariyasaccāni yathābhūtaṃ "
"abhisambojjhanti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn56.5:3.1"
msgid ""
"Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, ‘idaṃ dukkhan’ti yogo karaṇīyo … pe … ‘ayaṃ "
"dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’ti yogo karaṇīyo”ti."
msgstr "That’s why you should practice meditation …”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn56.5:3.2"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ."
msgstr ""
